16:17.783 --> 16:19.866
they also get together just to share ideas. The 
second thing that's emerged from that is a group

16:22.110 --> 16:25.635
called assets. which is an association of the 
scientists and engineers and technicians out

16:25.902 --> 16:29.966
here. And they meet four or five times a year on a 
fairly informal basis. They'll have somebody

16:36.932 --> 16:42.418
come in as a lecturer, and they'll have beer 
together or lunch together. And that is an

16:42.618 --> 16:47.863
organization that recently got started, and 
we're delighted about that. And you had no role,

16:48.483 --> 16:52.467
basically, in starting those kind of 
arrangements?

